\par }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 [Psa 82:6]}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830  I have said, Ye are gods; and all of you are children of the most High. 
\par }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 [John 10:34-36]}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830  Jesus answered them, Is it not written in your law, I said, Ye are gods? }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 \{35\}}{
\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830  If he called them gods, unto whom the word of God came, and the scripture cannot be broken; }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 \{36\}}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 
