The scripture uses many names and figures
 of speech metaphorically. Scripture mentions God having hands, and feet and eyes, and we know that He does not literally possess these carnal body parts. These names are used to signify attributes of God, as far as limited human language can convey. 

\par In the same way, referring to men as "gods" conveys the exalted moral state that man can obtain through struggle and struggle and submission to God in all things. 
\par The scripture also admits the use of "gods' to refer to the idols and demons that false religions believe in: 
\par }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 [Psa 96:5]}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830  For all the gods of the nations are idols: but the LORD made the heavens. 
\par [Exo 20:3-5] Thou shalt have no other gods before me. }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 \{4\}}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830  Thou shalt not make unto thee any graven image, or any likeness of any thing that is in heaven ab
ove, or that is in the earth beneath, or that is in the water under the earth: }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 \{5\}}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 
 Thou shalt not bow down thyself to them, nor serve them: for I the LORD thy God am a jealous God, visiting the iniquity of the fathers upon the children unto the third and fourth generation of them that hate me; 
\par [Lev 17:7] And they shall no more offer their sacrifices unto devils, after whom they have gone a whoring. This shall be a statute for ever unto them throughout their generations. 
\par [Deu 32:16-17] They provoked him to jealousy with strange gods, with abominations provoked they him to anger. }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 \{17\}}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 
 They sacrificed unto devils, not to God; to gods whom they knew not, to new gods that came newly up, whom your fathers feared not. 
\par }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 [Psa 106:37-38]}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830  Yea, they sacrificed their sons and their daughters unto devils, }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 \{38\}}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 
