\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830  Thou knowest my downsitting and mine uprising, thou understandest my thought afar off. }{\cs54\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 \{3\}}{\fs32\insrsid6452859\charrsid6291830 
