The Symbol of Faith confesses the Holy Trinity. What is the first scriptural reference which begins to reveal the Holy Trinity? 
\par }\pard\plain \s1\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid6452859 \b\fs48\lang1033\langfe1033\kerning36\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid6452859 ANSWER 23
